Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
Last updated: 09-25-2024
HWY Enigma LLC
("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use our application
Pixel Converter Pro
, which is available on the iOS App Store.
1. Information We Collect
Personal Information:
We do not collect or store any personal information such as your name, email address, or phone number through the app.
Non-Personal Information:
We may collect non-personal information, such as app usage data or technical information (device type, operating system version) for improving the performance of the app. This data is anonymized and cannot be linked to any specific individual.
In-App Purchases:
If you make an in-app purchase to unlock PRO features, the purchase is processed through Apple's App Store. We do not collect or have access to your payment details. Apple may collect information as per their privacy policy. Please review Apple's privacy policy for more information on their data handling practices.
2. How We Use Your Information
The app collects information solely for:
Improving app functionality.
Processing in-app purchases.
Enhancing the user experience (such as saving your theme preferences).
3. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect the information we collect within the app from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no security system is impenetrable, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.
4. Children's Privacy
This app is not intended for use by children under the age of 4, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
5. Your Choices
As we do not collect any personal data directly, there are no specific opt-out options for personal data collection. For in-app purchases, you can manage or disable purchases through your Apple account settings.
6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a new "Last updated" date.
7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
HWY Enigma LLC
contact@hwyenigma.com
https://hwyenigma.com/
